{"_id":"BxYF2EeqOjtsAxja","name":"Tracking","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The denizen is excellent at tracking others by scent or using another sense. Treat its adventuring skill at three times the normal level for tests involving tracking.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223115,"modifiedTime":1662411890991,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"Gljx55OGyM7ZmvqY","name":"Flying","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>Using wings, engines or similar, this denizen can fly. Treat this as normal movement, but ignoring barriers that can be flown over at the game master's discretion. This being cannot be engaged in melee combat whilst flying unless it chooses to attack, in which case it can be targeted.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223116,"modifiedTime":1662411890992,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"IT8UNVu5KTqltzMn","name":"Puppet","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The being has no will of its own and must be directed by another mind. In consequence, it never surrenders or flees and will fight until destroyed.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223116,"modifiedTime":1662411890993,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"LjzDkN254JV7lrYs","name":"Energy attack","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The being has an energy attack that they can use once a round that ignores armour.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223117,"modifiedTime":1662411890993,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"NMjQXY2r3kn2JdEk","name":"Warp manifestations","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The being is able to utilise warp glyphs. The games master should feel free to assign the creature glyphs that reflect its power. It uses stamina to cast spells and requires a Warp focus skill check.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223118,"modifiedTime":1662411890994,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"Q6EuVTrS5AmNMRgP","name":"Brittle","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>This denizen is susceptible to impact damage. If smashing weapons or guns attack them successfully, the damage is rolled twice and the higher value is applied.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223119,"modifiedTime":1662411890994,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"RO81Vt0zhim8dOIV","name":"Dissolve","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>This being is able to dissolve matter, or exudes an acidic venom. All successful attacks cause it to splash out the venom, and any time it is successfully struck in melee the attacker must test their luck. On a fail, their weapon is destroyed.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223119,"modifiedTime":1662411890995,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"egcXNZtBqaWvPlHn","name":"Warp denizen","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>This creature does not exist in the material plane. It can only be harmed by warp-based attacks such as glyphs, and can pass through solid barriers such as doors and walls with ease.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223120,"modifiedTime":1662411890995,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"lRPBCjyFjVAPS8NP","name":"Formless","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The body of this denizen has no real form, so it may slide under doors, squeeze through narrow spaces etc. as if it were a thick, viscous liquid.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223121,"modifiedTime":1662411890996,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"mCu8DrIJqprSeDbV","name":"Poisonous","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>This denizen carries a poison or can inject a venom. If it successfully hits a target, the victim must test their luck. If they fail, the victim is poisoned, and loses [[/roll 1d6]] stamina at the start of each of the next [[/roll 1d3]] rounds. Poison or venom effects from the same source are not cumulative, although of course the creature can still inflict its normal damage when it hits.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223122,"modifiedTime":1662411890996,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
{"_id":"qrwCqsvK7MVZpwtm","name":"Regenerating","type":"Ability","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>The being is able to recover damage. Every round the being regains [[/roll 1d6]] stamina, up to a maximum of its starting value.</p>"},"ownership":{"default":0,"XMfgoFiiE1BZBDoZ":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"warlock","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.284","createdTime":1662145223124,"modifiedTime":1662411890997,"lastModifiedBy":"6R9Y3cM97XtOXeBn"}}
